  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">AFG ESNFI 13317 (  Winterization and Shelter Response in Qadis District of Badghis Province)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Key humanitarian interventions of the project will be: 
1. Distribution of cash for heating/fuel to 1100 HHs
2. Distribution of cash for emergency NFIs to 1100 HHs
3. Distribution of cash for transportation for voluntarily return to the place origin (from Kharistan IDP site to Qadis district) to 400 HHs
4. Distribution of cash for shelter/house upgrade/repair to 400 newly returned HHs in Qadis district
5. Provision of 257 awareness-raising sessions on GBV, Protection and Psychosocial Support</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">life saving for affected 1100 families and change their life and better condition for living .</narrative>
